0:The ally will clear the islands. With these heavily armed ships we will sink the enemy ships occupying these waters.
1:To the southeast, an enemy fleet has been spotted. If we play our cards right, we can destroy it. Otherwise, it will destroy us.
2:All aboard. The ally will destroy their ships and we will search the islands where infantry units may be located. We will transport our brave soldiers for this purpose.
3:To load units onto a ship, simply select the appropriate unit, press the boat icon, and then the target ship.Select the ship, then press the boat with arrow button on the left side of the screen to unload units.
